    <p>Before we get acquainted here is the low-down:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <p>
          <em>Timing:</em>
          We're fully booked until the <em>beginning of October 2016</em>, but we'd still love to hear from you if you've got an idea you think we can help with.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
